HEADWORD: Attestant
<hw>At*tes"tant</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>a
person who attests to the genuineness of a document or signature by
adding their own signature.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> witness.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

